Additional classes for yarn details. Added specific yarn details to project page.

Push should be working for: * Date started * Date finished * Made for * Status * Tags * Size * Needles/Hooks

fixes #3 RecyclerView was overlaying the button on project, since relative layout only had the recyclerview above the button bar on stash view.
